1
00:00:08,014 --> 00:00:09,925
[RINGS CHIMING]

2
00:01:05,448 --> 00:01:06,654
[GRUNTS]

3
00:01:09,243 --> 00:01:11,161
MALE VOICE: <i>So, I know
what you're thinking.</i>

4
00:01:11,245 --> 00:01:13,407
<i>Why is that incredibly handsome hedgehog</i>

5
00:01:13,497 --> 00:01:17,161
<i>being chased by a madman
with a mustache from the Civil War?</i>

6
00:01:17,251 --> 00:01:20,995
<i>Well, to be honest, it feels like
I've been running my whole life.</i>

7
00:01:21,089 --> 00:01:23,547
<i>Is this too much? Am I going too fast?</i>

8
00:01:23,634 --> 00:01:26,467
<i>It's kind of what I do...
You know what? Let's back up.</i>

9
00:01:26,553 --> 00:01:29,261
[MIMICKING REVERSE AUDIO]

10
00:01:30,974 --> 00:01:34,183
["FRIENDS" BY HYPER POTIONS PLAYS]

11
00:01:34,269 --> 00:01:36,977
<i>This is the island where I'm from.</i>

12
00:01:37,898 --> 00:01:39,388
<i>It had everything.</i>

13
00:01:39,483 --> 00:01:41,815
<i>Sandy beaches, cascading waterfalls,</i>

14
00:01:41,902 --> 00:01:43,768
<i>public access to loop-de-loops.</i>

15
00:01:43,862 --> 00:01:45,697
<i>And, I never had to catch a school bus</i>

16
00:01:45,781 --> 00:01:48,022
<i>because I could run
across the entire island</i>

17
00:01:48,116 --> 00:01:49,902
<i>in less than two seconds.</i>

18
00:01:49,993 --> 00:01:51,734
<i>Also, there was no school.</i>

19
00:01:51,828 --> 00:01:53,944
<i>I know, pretty sweet island, right?</i>

20
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:55,621
Yeah!

21
00:01:55,707 --> 00:01:59,826
<i>I was born with extraordinary powers
and was told to keep them secret.</i>

22
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:02,537
<i>And like any kid,
I did the exact opposite.</i>

23
00:02:02,631 --> 00:02:03,712
BABY SONIC: Whoo-hoo!

24
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:07,883
SONIC: <i>That's Longclaw.
She took care of me.</i>

25
00:02:07,969 --> 00:02:12,429
<i>She was basically Obi-Wan Kenobi
if Obi-Wan Kenobi had a beak and ate mice.</i>

26
00:02:12,516 --> 00:02:15,054
Sonic, someone could have seen you.

27
00:02:15,144 --> 00:02:17,806
No one saw me. I'm too fast!

28
00:02:17,897 --> 00:02:19,808
And I wanted to bring you this.

29
00:02:19,899 --> 00:02:21,355
[SIGHS]

30
00:02:21,442 --> 00:02:22,523
[GASPS]

31
00:02:23,736 --> 00:02:24,976
Get down!

32
00:02:28,616 --> 00:02:32,200
SONIC: <i>Turns out, with great power
comes great power-hungry bad guys.</i>

33
00:02:32,286 --> 00:02:34,277
<i>And I led them right to us.</i>

34
00:02:36,833 --> 00:02:38,244
[GRUNTING]

35
00:02:38,334 --> 00:02:40,075
[ARROWS WHISTLING]

36
00:02:42,714 --> 00:02:43,670
[YELLS]

37
00:02:44,674 --> 00:02:46,506
[BOTH GRUNTING]

38
00:02:49,095 --> 00:02:50,295
Listen carefully, Sonic.

39
00:02:51,764 --> 00:02:54,722
You have a power unlike
anything I have ever seen.

40
00:02:54,809 --> 00:02:57,141
And that means someone
will always want it.

41
00:02:57,228 --> 00:03:00,937
The only way to stay safe
is to stay hidden.

42
00:03:04,527 --> 00:03:07,144
This world is on the far side
of the universe.

43
00:03:07,238 --> 00:03:08,525
You should be safe there.

44
00:03:08,615 --> 00:03:11,357
-I don't want to go without you.
-You must.

45
00:03:11,452 --> 00:03:14,035
These rings will be your most
important possession.

46
00:03:14,121 --> 00:03:15,521
-[PURSUERS SHOUTING]
-[GASPS]

47
00:03:16,331 --> 00:03:17,787
[ALL PANTING]

48
00:03:17,875 --> 00:03:20,458
If you're ever discovered, use one.

49
00:03:20,544 --> 00:03:22,911
Never stop running.

50
00:03:23,589 --> 00:03:24,954
Now go!

51
00:03:27,468 --> 00:03:28,674
[ALL SHOUTING]

52
00:03:28,761 --> 00:03:29,922
Longclaw!

53
00:03:31,555 --> 00:03:32,590
Goodbye, Sonic.

54
00:03:32,681 --> 00:03:33,637
No!

55
00:03:33,724 --> 00:03:35,556
-[GASPING]
-[ELECTRICITY CRACKLING]

56
00:03:35,642 --> 00:03:37,428
No!

57
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:41,937
[PANTING]

58
00:04:03,421 --> 00:04:04,877
Come on, one car?

59
00:04:09,761 --> 00:04:12,298
[MAKING FAST CAR NOISES]

