66
00:04:25,819 --> 00:04:27,403
That's amazing. Please send pics.

67
00:04:27,487 --> 00:04:29,524
No, Wade. I'm at the speed trap.

68
00:04:29,614 --> 00:04:32,777
Already? How did you get back so fast?
Barbados is in the ocean!

69
00:04:32,867 --> 00:04:34,608
Hang on, I think I got something.

70
00:04:39,290 --> 00:04:40,530
[BEEPING]

71
00:04:41,793 --> 00:04:44,785
Hey, buddy! Where's the fire?

72
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:46,665
Got kids living around here.

73
00:04:47,757 --> 00:04:50,294
I thought that was kind of funny.
Sorry. [CHUCKLES]

74
00:04:53,096 --> 00:04:54,962
-[WHOOSHING]
-[RADAR BEEPS]

75
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:57,681
What?

76
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,470
[CLICKS]

77
