78
00:05:36,765 --> 00:05:38,683
WADE [OVER RADIO]:
<i>Tom, we need you down on Main Street.</i>

79
00:05:38,767 --> 00:05:40,602
<i>There's been a violent gang shoot-out.</i>

80
00:05:40,686 --> 00:05:42,643
