-[WADE LAUGHS]

81
00:05:42,730 --> 00:05:45,392
<i>Just kidding. A duck stole a bagel.</i>

82
00:05:45,482 --> 00:05:47,564
<i>But they do need it back.</i>

83
00:05:58,788 --> 00:06:01,415
Whoa, buddy, you almost
got yourself killed out there.

84
00:06:01,499 --> 00:06:03,543
What are you,
some kind of adrenaline junkie?

85
00:06:03,627 --> 00:06:05,709
It must be rough being slow all the time.

86
00:06:05,795 --> 00:06:09,083
Tell you what. Today is your lucky day.

87
00:06:09,174 --> 00:06:11,415
["DON'T STOP ME NOW" BY QUEEN PLAYS]

88
00:06:11,509 --> 00:06:13,466
SONIC: Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

89
00:06:13,553 --> 00:06:15,885
Have you ever felt so alive?

90
00:06:17,307 --> 00:06:19,799
This is great. You're doing amazing.

91
00:06:19,893 --> 00:06:21,383
Oh, geez!

92
00:06:21,937 --> 00:06:23,894
Good recovery.

93
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,721
Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

94
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:28,818
-Let's keep this our little secret, okay?
-[RATTLING]

95
00:06:28,902 --> 00:06:32,065
You never saw me. I was never here.

96
00:06:32,155 --> 00:06:34,146
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

97
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,127
SONIC: <i>So what were you expecting?</i>

98
00:06:48,214 --> 00:06:52,208
<i>A dirty little hedgehog eating berries
and struggling to survive?</i>

99
00:06:52,301 --> 00:06:56,795
<i>Think again. Because I am
living my best life on Earth.</i>

100
00:06:56,889 --> 00:06:58,550
<i>I've got a library</i>

101
00:07:00,101 --> 00:07:01,762
<i>a home gym,</i>

102
00:07:01,852 --> 00:07:04,435
<i>and a state-of-the-art security system.</i>

103
00:07:04,522 --> 00:07:05,762
[GRUNTS]

104
00:07:05,856 --> 00:07:08,723
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

105
00:07:16,659 --> 00:07:17,649
Oh, no.

106
00:07:19,078 --> 00:07:22,122
<i>And, if I'm ever discovered,
I'll follow Longclaw's instructions</i>

107
00:07:22,206 --> 00:07:25,039
<i>and use my rings
to escape to a new planet.</i>

108
00:07:25,584 --> 00:07:29,293
<i>A nice, safe little world
filled only with mushrooms.</i>

109
00:07:30,881 --> 00:07:33,794
<i>Gross, smelly mushrooms.</i>

110
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,421
I hate mushrooms.

111
00:07:37,806 --> 00:07:39,888
<i>But let's not worry about all that.</i>

112
00:07:39,975 --> 00:07:44,390
<i>This is Green Hills,
the greatest place on Earth.</i>

113
00:07:45,772 --> 00:07:48,184
<i>These are my people and, dare I say,</i>

114
00:07:48,275 --> 00:07:50,687
<i>I am their lovable space creature.</i>

115
00:07:50,777 --> 00:07:52,609
<i>So what if they don't know I exist?</i>

116
00:07:54,573 --> 00:07:57,782
<i>My favorite person is the Donut Lord,</i>

117
00:07:58,702 --> 00:08:00,943
<i>protector of this town</i>

118
00:08:01,038 --> 00:08:04,030
<i>and defender of all creatures,
big and small.</i>

119
00:08:04,124 --> 00:08:05,114
