120
00:08:05,208 --> 00:08:06,994
Donald. Daisy. Daffy.

121
00:08:08,211 --> 00:08:10,669
<i>Donut Lord lives with Pretzel Lady.</i>

122
00:08:11,339 --> 00:08:12,921
<i>She is super nice to animals</i>

123
00:08:13,008 --> 00:08:16,467
<i>and strangely was born without bones.</i>

124
00:08:16,553 --> 00:08:18,043
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

125
00:08:18,138 --> 00:08:19,845
<i>There is one person in town</i>

126
00:08:19,931 --> 00:08:21,349
-<i>who's actually onto me.</i>
-[LAUGHING]

127
00:08:21,433 --> 00:08:23,640
[CHUCKLING] <i>He calls me the blue devil.</i>

128
00:08:23,727 --> 00:08:25,593
I almost caught him last night.

129
00:08:25,687 --> 00:08:27,519
SONIC: <i>Say hello to Crazy Carl.</i>

130
00:08:27,606 --> 00:08:29,347
-[WHOOSHING]
-[YELPS]

131
00:08:29,983 --> 00:08:31,099
[TRAPS SNAPPING]

132
00:08:31,194 --> 00:08:32,605
SONIC: <i>We have fun together.</i>

133
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,269
[GRUNTS]

134
00:08:34,363 --> 00:08:36,855
I know you're out there!

135
00:08:36,949 --> 00:08:39,862
And I know you're real!

136
00:08:39,952 --> 00:08:42,489
SONIC: No, I'm not!

137
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:44,662
<i>Movie night is my favorite.</i>

138
00:08:44,749 --> 00:08:47,161
Please, please, please, please, please.

139
00:08:47,251 --> 00:08:48,707
Yes! Keanu!

140
00:08:48,795 --> 00:08:50,411
You are a national treasure.

141
00:08:50,505 --> 00:08:52,872
-<i>When If ind you...</i>
-MAN: <i>Pop quiz, hotshot.</i>

142
00:08:52,965 --> 00:08:54,706
<i>There's a bomb on a bus.</i>

143
00:08:54,801 --> 00:08:56,667
"Pop quiz, hotshot." [KISSES]

144
00:08:56,761 --> 00:08:58,547
-It's a classic line.
-[LAUGHING]

145
00:08:58,638 --> 00:09:00,595
SONIC: <i>Basically, we're like a family.</i>

146
00:09:01,307 --> 00:09:03,093
<i>Even though we haven't met yet.</i>

147
00:09:03,184 --> 00:09:05,102
SONIC [IN GERMAN ACCENT]:
You don't zink your

148
00:09:05,186 --> 00:09:07,688
