you a bit crazy perhaps?

149
00:09:07,772 --> 00:09:09,683
[CHUCKLES] Crazy? Me?

150
00:09:09,774 --> 00:09:12,357
No way, Doc. You got me all wrong.

151
00:09:12,443 --> 00:09:16,812
And despite all these so-called friends
of yours, deep down,

152
00:09:16,906 --> 00:09:19,106
