...you're still rather lonely?

153
00:09:22,995 --> 00:09:24,451
[LAUGHING]

154
00:09:24,539 --> 00:09:27,953
<i>Perhaps afraid you'll be alone forever?</i>

155
00:09:33,423 --> 00:09:35,209
[CHITTERING]

156
00:09:37,219 --> 00:09:39,756
[HORN HONKING]

157
00:09:42,224 --> 00:09:45,967
Uh-uh. Hey! No, no, no, no.

158
00:09:46,061 --> 00:09:47,677
Get out of there. Come on.

159
00:09:47,771 --> 00:09:50,103
Oh, come on! Get out of there!

160
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:52,602
