-Is that what I think it is?
-Uh-huh. Open it.

167
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:12,042
Oh, it's kind of small. Is that bad?

168
00:10:12,129 --> 00:10:13,836
Just open it.

169
00:10:19,012 --> 00:10:20,594
[EXHALES] "Dear Thomas,

170
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:23,516
We have reviewed your application
to the San Francisco Police Department,

171
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:26,268
and pending interdepartmental review
and background check,

172
