177
00:10:37,697 --> 00:10:39,483
Oh! [GROANS]

178
00:10:39,574 --> 00:10:40,564
Wrong one!

179
00:10:42,827 --> 00:10:44,738
Ta-da! [LAUGHS]

180
00:10:45,788 --> 00:10:48,576
-You never had a doubt, huh?
-No! Mm-mmm.

181
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:54,043
-I can't believe this.
-Oh, I know! You did it.

182
00:10:55,757 --> 00:10:57,168
Hey, what are those?

183
00:10:58,426 --> 00:11:00,793
