223
00:12:52,334 --> 00:12:53,916
[CROWD CHEERING]

224
00:12:55,295 --> 00:12:57,878
[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

225
00:13:33,626 --> 00:13:36,368
Oh! So cool.

226
00:13:41,384 --> 00:13:42,551
Bottom of the ninth, tie score.

227
00:13:42,635 --> 00:13:46,173
And exactly who you want at the plate
with the game on the line: Sonic!

228
00:13:46,263 --> 00:13:48,056
But staring him down
from the pitcher's mound

229
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:51,349
is the most fearsome southpaw
in Green Hills:

230
00:13:51,435 --> 00:13:52,800
Also Sonic.

231
00:13:52,895 --> 00:13:54,352
Okay. Focus, Sonic.

232
00:13:54,439 --> 00:13:57,789
If you win this game, you'll be
the most beloved kid in Green Hills.

233
